<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 09:11:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾敦促中国不要改变金门群岛附近海域的“现状”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-china-not-change-status-quo-around-waters-near-kinmen-islands-2024-03-08/</link><description>台湾陆委会周五敦促中国不要通过派遣海警船进入禁区来改变台湾控制的金门群岛附近海域的“现状”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 08:34:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-china-not-change-status-quo-around-waters-near-kinmen-islands-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>收购目标 Currys 表示希腊资产处置将于四月完成</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/takeover-target-currys-says-greek-disposal-will-complete-april-2024-03-08/</link><description>处于潜在收购战中心的英国电器零售商 Currys 周五表示，在获得希腊当局批准后，出售其希腊子公司的交易将于 4 月上半月完成。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:41:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/takeover-target-currys-says-greek-disposal-will-complete-april-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部表示，印度在边境增兵不会缓解紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/more-indian-troops-border-wont-ease-tensions-says-china-foreign-ministry-2024-03-08/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周五在例行新闻发布会上表示，中方认为印度在中印争议边境增兵的举动“不利于缓解紧张局势”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:39:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/more-indian-troops-border-wont-ease-tensions-says-china-foreign-ministry-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>第23条：香港新国安法你需要了解的事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/article-23-what-you-need-know-about-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-08/</link><description>经过上周结束的为期一个月的公众咨询后，香港政府于周五公布了拟议的国家安全法案。市领导希望该法案能够迅速获得通过，可能在几周内获得通过。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 07:36:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/article-23-what-you-need-know-about-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚失踪的 MH370 飞机：10 年后我们所知道的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-missing-mh370-plane-what-we-know-10-years-2024-03-08/</link><description>十年前，载有 239 名乘客的马来西亚航空公司 MH370 航班失踪，至今仍然是世界上最大的航空谜团之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 06:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-missing-mh370-plane-what-we-know-10-years-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因中国改革和人工智能激增而吸引大量外国资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-draw-massive-foreign-funds-chinas-reforms-ai-surge-2024-03-08/</link><description>随着北京推出改革措施以及人工智能（AI）热潮推动科技股飙升，中国股市出现反弹，外国投资者在二月份向亚洲股市注入了大量资金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 06:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-draw-massive-foreign-funds-chinas-reforms-ai-surge-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>1-2月中国电动汽车销量放缓；降价力度加大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-sales-slow-january-february-competition-intensifies-2024-03-08/</link><description>周五的行业数据显示，中国电动汽车销量在今年头几个月放缓，随着市场领导者比亚迪带头进行更大幅度的降价，竞争加剧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:35:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-sales-slow-january-february-competition-intensifies-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>打拳抽铁，中国女子走“YOLO”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/punching-pumping-iron-chinese-women-go-yolo-2024-03-08/</link><description>一名 30 多岁的女性没有工作、没有朋友，也没有人生方向，她决定开始打拳击，引发了身体上的转变，这是今年中国票房最高的电影的故事。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/punching-pumping-iron-chinese-women-go-yolo-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国恒大清算人任命法律顾问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-liquidators-appoint-legal-advisers-sources-say-2024-03-08/</link><description>据直接了解情况的消息人士透露，中国恒大的清算人已聘请三家律师事务所就这家陷入困境的房地产巨头的清盘程序提供咨询。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:20:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-liquidators-appoint-legal-advisers-sources-say-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>债券受托人成为清算中国开发商佳兆业的新申请人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bond-trustee-becomes-new-petitioner-liquidate-china-developer-kaisa-2024-03-08/</link><description>在主要美元债券持有人的指示下，债券受托人取代了原申请人后，香港一家法院将中国房地产开发商佳兆业集团清算听证会推迟至 4 月 29 日。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bond-trustee-becomes-new-petitioner-liquidate-china-developer-kaisa-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴旗下灵犀游戏表示，管理层将辞职，为年轻高管让路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibabas-lingxi-games-says-management-step-down-make-way-younger-execs-2024-03-08/</link><description>一份内部备忘录显示，阿里巴巴集团旗下视频游戏部门灵犀游戏已告知员工，其领导团队将辞职，为更年轻的管理层让路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 05:12:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/alibabas-lingxi-games-says-management-step-down-make-way-younger-execs-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社报道，华为、中芯国际使用美国技术制造先进芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-smic-used-us-tech-make-advanced-chips-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-08/</link><description>据彭博社援引知情人士的话报道，中国公司华为技术有限公司和中芯国际公司将于 2023 年使用美国技术在中国生产先进芯片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-smic-used-us-tech-make-advanced-chips-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市创7个月新高，美国就业数据成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-08/</link><description>亚洲股市周五升至七个月高点，并迎来两个多月来最坚挺的一周，投资者对主要央行主导的降息周期即将到来的前景感到欢呼，使美元和国债收益率承压。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国海油在南海发现亿吨级油田</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-makes-100-million-ton-oilfield-discovery-south-china-sea-2024-03-08/</link><description>中国国有石油天然气巨头中海油周五在一份声明中表示，该公司在南海发现了一个新的储量，探明储量超过 1 亿吨石油当量。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-makes-100-million-ton-oilfield-discovery-south-china-sea-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国最高立法者承诺维护主权和安全利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-legislators-safeguard-sovereignty-security-interests-2024-03-08/</link><description>中国最高立法者周五誓言要颁布一系列新法律，以“实现中国国家安全体系和能力的现代化”，同时维护主权利益，一些分析人士称，这表明中国更加关注已知的安全威胁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-legislators-safeguard-sovereignty-security-interests-2024-03-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>